}</style><article id="post-18201" class="post-18201 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-all-recipes category-american category-chicken category-dinner category-main-course category-skillet infinite-scroll-item no-featured-image-padding" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" itemscope><div class="inside-article"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</h1></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-snippet wprm-recipe-template-snippet-basic-buttons"><a href="#recipe" data-recipe="18195" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path data-color="color-2" d="M9,2h6c0.6,0,1-0.4,1-1s-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,0,8,0.4,8,1S8.4,2,9,2z"></path> <path fill="#ffffff" d="M16,11V5c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,4,8,4.4,8,5v6H1.9L12,23.6L22.1,11H16z"></path></g></svg></span> Jump to Recipe</a><a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wprm_print/chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-print wprm-recipe-link wprm-print-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-print-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent" data-recipe-id="18195" data-template="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-print-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="16px" height="16px" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g ><path fill="#ffffff" d="M19,5.09V1c0-0.552-0.448-1-1-1H6C5.448,0,5,0.448,5,1v4.09C2.167,5.569,0,8.033,0,11v7c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h4v4c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h12c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-4h4c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-7C24,8.033,21.833,5.569,19,5.09z M7,2h10v3H7V2z M17,22H7v-9h10V22z M18,10c-0.552,0-1-0.448-1-1c0-0.552,0.448-1,1-1s1,0.448,1,1C19,9.552,18.552,10,18,10z"/></g></svg></span> Print Recipe</a></div><p><strong>Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</strong> is the ultimate creamy pasta recipe that brings together smoky bacon, tender chicken, and tangy ranch in one comforting skillet. This easy dinner idea is ready in about 35 minutes, making it a perfect family favorite meal for busy weeknights. I love how it uses simple ingredients you can find in any grocery store to create a cheesy ranch pasta dish that everyone asks for again and again.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-122" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_page_title"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(122); });</script><img decoding="async" class="gb-media-12a372fb" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta.webp" alt="Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta recipe finished dish" title="Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta recipe" /><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="why-love-box"><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="your-new-weeknight-hero">Your New Weeknight Hero &#x1F958;</h2><ul><li><strong>Quick &#038; Satisfying</strong> &#x2013; You can have this creamy pasta recipe on the table in just over half an hour.</li><li><strong>Pantry-Friendly Ingredients</strong> &#x2013; This family favorite meal builds flavor with staples you likely already have.</li><li><strong>One-Skillet Simplicity</strong> &#x2013; Cook your pasta, then use the same pan for the sauce to minimize cleanup.</li><li><strong>Crowd-Pleasing Flavor</strong> &#x2013; The combination of ranch, cheese, and bacon is a guaranteed hit with both kids and adults.</li></ul></div><div class="wp-block-rank-math-toc-block" id="rank-math-toc"><h2>Table of Contents</h2><nav><ul><li><a href="#from-fridge-to-table-in-a-flash">From Fridge to Table in a Flash</a></li><li><a href="#thoughtful-tips-for-special-diets">Thoughtful Tips for Special Diets</a></li><li><a href="#my-pro-tips-for-the-best-chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta">My Pro Tips for the Best Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</a></li><li><a href="#nutrition-and-health-benefits">Nutrition and Health Benefits</a></li><li><a href="#a-lighter-version-of-this-chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta">A Lighter Version of This Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</a></li><li><a href="#how-to-serve-your-chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta">How to Serve Your Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</a></li><li><a href="#common-mistakes-and-how-to-avoid-them">Common Mistakes (And How to Avoid Them)</a></li><li><a href="#how-to-store-and-reheat-your-leftovers">How to Store and Reheat Your Leftovers</a></li><li><a href="#more-cozy-comfort-food-dinners">More Cozy Comfort Food Dinners</a></li></ul></nav></div><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-youll-need-for-your-chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta">What You&#x2019;ll Need for Your <strong>Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</strong></h2><section class="ingredient-group" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Pasta &#038; Protein</h3><ul style="list-style: disc; margin:0 0 18px 20px; line-height:1.8;"><li><strong>Penne pasta</strong> &#8211; The perfect shape for holding the creamy sauce in every bite.</li><li><strong>Bacon</strong> &#8211; Adds a crispy, smoky flavor throughout the entire dish.</li><li><strong>Chicken breasts</strong> &#8211; Tender protein cut into bite-sized pieces for easy eating.</li></ul><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-130" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_first_paragraph"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(130); });</script></section><section class="ingredient-group" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Signature Sauce</h3><ul style="list-style: disc; margin:0 0 18px 20px; line-height:1.8;"><li><strong>Ranch dressing</strong> &#8211; The creamy, tangy flavor base that makes this recipe special.</li><li><strong>Cheddar cheese</strong> &#8211; Melts into the sauce for extra richness and cheesy goodness.</li><li><strong>Milk &#038; flour</strong> &#8211; These combine to create a smooth, velvety sauce that coats the pasta perfectly.</li><li><strong>Butter &#038; seasonings</strong> &#8211; Garlic powder, onion powder, salt, and pepper build a deep, savory flavor.</li></ul></section><img decoding="async" class="gb-media-b9578a36" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Delicious-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta.webp" alt="Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta ingredients preparation" title="Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta ingredients" /><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="from-fridge-to-table-in-a-flash">From Fridge to Table in a Flash</h2><p>I promise this <strong>Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</strong> respects your busy schedule. With just 15 minutes of prep and 20 minutes of cook time, your total time investment is only 35 minutes. Honestly, that&#x2019;s less time than it takes to decide on takeout.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-131" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_second_paragraph"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(131); });</script><p>This quick weeknight dinner comes together so smoothly. You can boil the pasta while the bacon and chicken cook in your skillet. Then, the creamy sauce whisks up in minutes. It&#x2019;s the ideal timeline for a stress-free, family favorite meal. For another fantastic quick pasta fix, check out my <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/creamy-pasta/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">creamy pasta</a> recipe.</p><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="thoughtful-tips-for-special-diets">Thoughtful Tips for Special Diets</h2><p>As a home cook who loves making flavors accessible, I always think about adaptations. For those managing sugar intake or looking for more glucose-friendly options, this recipe can be tweaked easily. The primary sugar-conscious note here is in the ranch dressing, which often contains added sugars.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-132" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="mid_content"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(132); });</script><p>First, seek out a no added sugar or sugar-free ranch dressing at your store&#x2014;many great options exist. Second, you can control portions by serving this rich, cheesy ranch pasta alongside a large green salad to balance the meal. Finally, if you make your own ranch, you have full control and can use a natural sweetener like a touch of xylitol if needed.</p><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="my-pro-tips-for-the-best-chicken-bacon-ranch-pasta">My Pro Tips for the Best <strong>Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</strong></h2><p>After making this countless times, I&#x2019;ve gathered a few secrets that make a big difference. These tips will help you master this easy dinner idea on the very first try.</p><ul><li><strong>Boost the Herbs:</strong> Use a packet of dry ranch seasoning mix instead of just bottled dressing for a more potent, aromatic flavor.</li><li><strong>Go Gluten-Free:</strong> Swap the all-purpose flour for a 1:1 gluten-free blend and use your favorite GF pasta. The sauce will be just as creamy.</li><li><strong>Avoid Mushy Pasta:</strong> Cook your penne until it&#x2019;s just al dente. It will continue to soften slightly when tossed in the hot sauce, so this prevents it from becoming too soft. This is the same technique I use in my <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/spinach-ricotta-stuffed-shells/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stuffed shells</a>.</li><li><strong>Reheat Like a Pro:</strong> Leftovers reheat best with a splash of milk or broth in a saucepan over low heat, stirring gently to re-emulsify the sauce.</li></ul><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-133" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="long_content"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(133); });</script><p>Want another creamy, comforting dish that&#x2019;s just as simple? My <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/creamy-mac-and-cheese/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">creamy mac and cheese</a> uses a similar stovetop method for ultimate comfort.</p><p><div id="recipe"></div><div id="wprm-recipe-container-18195" class="wprm-recipe-container" data-recipe-id="18195" data-servings="4"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-template-ewpgls"><div class="wprm-recipe-image wprm-block-image-rounded"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: #666666;border-radius: 0px;width: 1000px;max-width: 100%;height: 400px;object-fit: cover;" width="896" height="1344" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta.webp" class="attachment-1000x999999 size-1000x999999" alt="Easy Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta" srcset="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta.webp 896w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta-200x300.webp 200w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta-683x1024.webp 683w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Easy-Chicken-Bacon-Ranch-Pasta-768x1152.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px" /></div><div class="wprm-layout-container wprm-padding-40"><div class="wprm-layout-column-container wprm-align-middle wprm-column-gap-10 wprm-column-rows-recipe-500"><div class="wprm-layout-column wprm-align-rows-center"><h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Chicken Bacon Ranch Pasta</h2></div><div class="wprm-layout-column wprm-align-right wprm-align-rows-center" style="--wprm-layout-column-text-color: var(--glacier-accent-color);">
