t-name">knife</div></li><li class="wprm-recipe-equipment-item" style="list-style-type: none;margin-left: 32px;"><div class="wprm-recipe-equipment-name">slotted spoon</div></li><li class="wprm-recipe-equipment-item" style="list-style-type: none;margin-left: 32px;"><div class="wprm-recipe-equipment-name">measuring spoons</div></li><li class="wprm-recipe-equipment-item" style="list-style-type: none;margin-left: 32px;"><div class="wprm-recipe-equipment-name">measuring cups</div></li><li class="wprm-recipe-equipment-item" style="list-style-type: none;margin-left: 32px;"><div class="wprm-recipe-equipment-name">stirring spoon</div></li></ul><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-134" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="longer_content"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(134); });</script></div></div><div id="recipe-18195-instructions" class="wprm-recipe-instructions-container wprm-recipe-18195-instructions-container wprm-block-text-normal" data-recipe="18195"><h3 class="wprm-recipe-header wprm-recipe-instructions-header wprm-block-text-bold wprm-align-left wprm-header-decoration-icon-line wprm-expandable-container-separated wprm-expandable-expanded" style="padding: 10px 20px;background-color: var(--glacier-header-background);"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
